This project is a responsive personal portfolio website built using HTML5, CSS3, and Bootstrap 4.

It features a modern hero/banner section with a navigation bar and adaptive layout that works seamlessly across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.

The design focuses on clarity, responsiveness, and clean UI structure, making it suitable for personal branding and frontend portfolios.

